Ibyago byo kwandura Coronavirus (COVID-19) mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, byongerewe kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) kigaragaza imimerere nk'iyo mu Burayi/Akarere k'ubukungu bwa Burayi n'u Bwongereza igaragaza ko, nubwo ku rwego rutandukanye bitewe n'igihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kigenda gitera imbere mu bihugu byose.
Dukurikije ibihamya bituruka mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye bigomba kongera imyiteguro yabo ku ndwara nyinshi za COVID-19 zizakenera ubuvuzi, cyane cyane kwita ku barwayi bakomeye.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, habonetse icyorezo cy'indwara z'ibihaha zitamenyekanye mu binyabuzima.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya indwara n'ivangura ry'indwara cyatangaje ko umugera ushyiraho icyorezo cya coronavirus cyiswe coronavirus yo mu buryo bw'ubuhumekero (SARS-COV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, icyorezo cy'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 cyiswe coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ubuhamya bugaragaza ko abagera kuri 80% by'abantu banduye COVID-19 bafite indwara y'ubuhumekero, ari yo ndwara y'imyenda yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ifite cyangwa idafite indwara y'ibihaha, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu bantu 14% banduye, COVID-19 igenda ihinduka indwara ikomeye igasaba kumara iminsi mu bitaro mu gihe abagera kuri 6% bagerwaho n'indwara ikomeye igasaba kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abapfa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 uri hejuru ya 4%.
Muri iki cyegeranyo, tugereranya impinduka ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cy'u Burayi / Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'u Bwongereza (Ubwongereza) tugereranyije n'iy'intara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Nanone, turagereranya umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza n'uw'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibimenyetso by'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi / EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'u Bushinwa, COVID-19 ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bihugu bitandukanye ndetse n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bihugu ku isi ubu kirimo gukurikira iki gihugu.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu nyandiko yo ku itariki ya 5 Werurwe 2020 ya Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. yatangajwe ko ari yo yabaye iya mbere mu Burayi yemeje icyorezo cya COVID-19 nk'uko bigaragara n'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS).
Mu karere ka EU/EEA, u Bufaransa bwagaragaje ku wa 24 Mutarama 2020 ko hari abantu batatu banduye mu bantu bagarutse mu Bushinwa bavuye i Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, COVID-19 imaze kugaragara mu bihugu 30 byose bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, aho hagati y'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 n'uwo munsi w'ubukwe, abantu 39,768 banduye n'abantu 1,727 bapfuye, n'abantu 17,750. abantu 1,441 bapfuye mu Butaliyani honyine.
Kubona umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 n'ibyabaye
Mu kigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya indwara z'ibyorezo (ECDC), imibare ya COVID-19 yamenyekanye mu gihugu cyose ku isi, igera ku nzego z'ibanze gusa nka Minisiteri y'Ubuzima y'Igihugu, inzego z'ubuzima z'igihugu ndetse na OMS na OMS, ihora ivugururwa buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma imiterere ya COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, ndetse agereranywa n'iy'u Butaliyani.
Nk'abashinzwe ibikorwa by'ikoranabuhanga mu kurwanya COVID-19, dusanga iminsi 14 y'ikoranabuhanga mu kurwanya COVID-19, bityo tukareba uko COVID-19 ikora mu bihugu byose by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza, hagati ya tariki ya 1 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twatangije kandi umubare w'abatangaza ko ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo, ku rwego rw'igihugu, ku wa 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020 mu gihe cy'igihugu cy'u Butaliyani.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Ihinduka ry'iminsi 14 ry'ibanze ry'ibimenyetso by'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange ryakozwe n'intara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Ifoto ya 1).
Ku rwego rw'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange, umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 watangiye kwiyongera ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, nyuma yaho ugera ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi).
Ibi byatewe n'umubare w'abanduye wavuye mu Butaliyani wiyongereye cyane, ariko ibihugu byose byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA n'u Bwongereza byerekana ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongereye cyane.
Mu ishusho ya 2 hagaragaza icyorezo cya COVID-19, mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'ibyo mu Butaliyani ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Igaragaza ko ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'ibihugu by'iburasirazuba bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, byari byamaze gutanga amakuru y'abanduye ugereranyije n'ab'u Butaliyani mu byumweru 3 cyangwa birenga.
Ubushakashatsi bwacu bugaragaza ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongera cyane muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibyavuzwe mu byaranze icyorezo cya COVID-19 byerekana ko icyorezo cyateye imbere mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Ibi nubwo ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, mu gusubiza ibibazo by'ubuzima bw'abaturage mu bihugu, ndetse wenda n'imanza zitandukanye mu bihugu hamwe n'amategeko atandukanye yo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba kugeragezwa kugira ngo bagaragaze ko bafite COVID-19, harimo no kugira ibizamini.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twugarijwe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani batangaje ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ibitaro n'ibigo byitabwaho cyane muri utwo turere byamaze kugera ku ntego zabo.
Amakuru ku barwayi bajyanywe mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 na/cyangwa ku kigo cy'ubuvuzi bukomeye ubu aboneka ku rwego rwa EU/EEA ku kigero cya 6% na 1% by'abanduye, hakurikijwe (amakuru ntabwo agaragaza).
Ariko kandi, ibyo bigomba gukoranywa mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga kugira ngo bihuze n'amakuru yo kugenzura abagwaho ubu, yibanda ku makuru y'abandura n'abapfa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2010-11 bwagaragaje ko hari itandukaniro rikomeye hagati y'uburwayi bw'ibanze n'ibitanda by'ibanze by'ibanze by'ibanze mu Burayi, kuva ku 29.2 mu Budage kugera ku 4.2 ku baturage 100,000 bo muri Porutugali.
