Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyateje icyorezo cy'indwara yo mu buryo bw'ubuhumekero (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000 kandi gifata abantu barenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, cyabaye icyorezo ku bantu.
Hari virusi imwe y'ubwandu, SARS-CoV, yateje SARS mu bihumbi by'abantu mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 nayo ishobora kwandura mu ndwara kandi igatera ibimenyetso nk'ibyo mu buryo bumwe na bumwe.
Ariko kandi, COVID-19 ifite ubukana buke cyane kandi ihitana abantu benshi kurusha SARS ariko ikwirakwira cyane kandi igera ku bantu bakuru kurusha abakiri bato n'abagabo kurusha abagore.
Kubera ko icyo kiganiro cyashubije umubare munini w'ibitabo byandikaga ku ndwara y'ihindagurika ry'ubwonko, cyagerageje gutanga ibitekerezo byumvikana ku birebana n'uko ikibazo cy'ubushakashatsi bw'ihindagurika cyagendaga gitera imbere.
Tuzamenya ibintu by'ibanze ku birebana n'indwara z'ibyorezo, indwara z'indwara, ubwandu, ubushakashatsi, ubuvuzi, kumenya uko indwara zizavuka (Prognosis), n'uburyo bwo kwirinda indwara.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko iki kiganiro kizafasha gusobanukirwa no kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Umunsi mukuru wo mu mpeshyi wo ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye urwibutso rutazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu rugo muri iyi minsi mikuru yose ndetse no mu byumweru byinshi nyuma y'icyorezo.
Iyi virusi ifitanye isano cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yatumye habaho icyorezo cy'indwara yo mu buryo bwo guhumeka (SARS) mu mwaka wa 2003; ku bw'ibyo, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryayise SARS-CoV-2 ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, kandi indwara ifitanye isano nayo yiswe CoV Coronavirus-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze gitangira gukwirakwira mu gihugu hose, kigera ku bandi 50 ku isi hose.
Kuva ku itariki ya 2 Werurwe 2020, iyi virusi yatumye abantu barenga 80,000 bagerwaho n'icyorezo cya COVID-19, abarwayi barenga 40,000 barakira ndetse abarwayi barenga 3,000 barapfa.
