Iyo ngingo igamije kugabanya uko ubushakashatsi buzaba bumeze mu ngingo nshya kandi yihuta.
Igihe cyose bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS hamwe na CoV yateje iki cyorezo, indwara yo guhumeka ku mpande z'abarabu (MERS, mu 2012).
Nanone turi busuzume ibyo tumaze kumenya ku birebana n'uburyo bwo kwirinda indwara, n'ibindi bibazo bikiriho.
