Igiterwa cy'umubiri cyitwa bAngiotensin enzyme ya 2 (ACE2) ni enzyme ifatanye n'uruhu rw'ingirabuzimafatizo mu mahaha, mu maraso, mu mutima, mu bwonko no mu mara.
ACE2 igenzura ibikorwa bya enzyme ihura n'imyanya y'ubudahangarwa (ACE) igabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II no kongera Ang (1-7) bigatuma iba intego ikomeye mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 kandi ikora nk'inzira yo kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za coronaviruses zimwe na zimwe.
Urubyiruko rw'abantu rwifashishije ingirabuzimafatizo yitwa hACE2.
Ingirabuzimafatizo y'umuriro ya Angiotensin 2 ni zinc irimo ironloenzyme iri hejuru y'urusobe rw'umubiri n'ibindi bice by'ingirabuzimafatizo.
Ingirabuzima fatizo ya ACE2 ikubiyemo igice cya N-terminal peptidase M2 n'igice cya C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transportar domain.
ACE2 ni ubwoko bw'imiterere y'amaraso y'umubiri, ifite igice cy'umuriro gikora ku mubiri kigaragaza imiterere y'ingirabuzimafatizo mu mahaha no mu bindi bice by'umubiri.
Ingingo z'umuriro z'umuriro wa ACE2 zituruka ku gice cy'umugera wa virusi cy'ikinyuranyo cyitwa enzyme, maze izo poroteyine z'umuriro zisohoka mu maraso, amaherezo zikajya mu maraso.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifatanisha uruhu rw'ibinyabuzima byinshi by'amaraso by'ubwoko bwa II bw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso, enterocyte zo mu mara, insoro z'amaraso n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'umutima n'ingingo z'umurava mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
ACE2 MRNA ishobora kuboneka mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko cy'ibere n'igice cy'ubwonko cy'ibere.
Umurimo wa mbere wa ACE2 ni ugushyiraho ingero zigereranya ACE.
ACE ikora ingufu za angiotensin I mu gutangiza angiotensin II.
ACE2 ikoresha carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine iva muri angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikayihindura hydrolyses mu gihumura gihumura angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora kuvanaho peptide zimwe na zimwe zirimo [des-Arg9] -bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi ihindagura imyenda ya SLC6A19 amino acid kandi ifitanye isano n'indwara ya Hartnup.
Nk'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima, ACE2 ikora nk'umuyoboro w'ingenzi wo kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo (Uruziga) za coronavirus zimwe na zimwe, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (umugera utuma habaho SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (umugera utuma habaho COVID-19).
Mu gihe cy'ubushakashatsi, abantu benshi bavuga ko ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima (spike s1 protein) z'ibinyabuzima (sars-cov) n'ibinyabuzima (sars-cov2) ziterwa n'ibinyabuzima (acetate) mu bice by'ingirabuzimafatizo (ACE2) bigaterwa n'ubushakashatsi bw'ibinyabuzima binini (cells) bigatuma umubiri ugira intandaro n'ubundi bwoko bw'indwara ndetse n'ingirabuzimafatizo (cells) mu bice by'ingirabuzimafatizo (cells).
